  In order to high-jack "localhost" and "127.0.0.1" addresses in firefox
    1. in the address bar of firefox type: about:config
    2. search for the "network.proxy.allow_hijacking_localhost"
    3. by default the value will be false. double click to change it to true
    4. check for the localhost site..

